@pluto999: Default for MP4box - 500 msec. I never delay nor preload audio track, because players which use Haali ignores that, in contrary, internal splitter of MPC and of VLC accept delay values. Therefore, I don't change nothing in interleave and corrections (if needed) are done either in audio-editor program or by DelayAudio in Avisynth.
